<i>Now that doesn't make any sense.</i>

01:05:23.254 --> 01:05:26.758
<i>Well, you haven't seen
as much of murder as I have, Mr. Cross.</i>

01:05:26.841 --> 01:05:30.303
<i>I'd rather have a judge give me the works
than have to do it myself.</i>

01:05:30.678 --> 01:05:31.930
<i>Right here in solitary.</i>

01:05:32.013 --> 01:05:33.098
<i>So what?</i>

01:05:33.181 --> 01:05:36.768
<i>So you go right on punishing yourself.
You can't get away with it.</i>

